<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Invoice - Order #<%= order.id %></title>
  <style media="print">
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    
    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #dc2626;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .company-info h1 {
      color: #dc2626;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    
    .company-info p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    
    .invoice-title {
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    .invoice-title h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .invoice-meta {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .meta-section h3 {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .meta-section p {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    
    .items-section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .items-section h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    
    table thead {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-top: 2px solid #dc2626;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #dc2626;
    }
    
    table th {
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #333;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    
    table td {
      padding: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    
    table tbody tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .text-right {
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    .summary-section {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    
    .summary {
      width: 300px;
    }
    
    .summary-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    
    .summary-row.total {
      border-top: 2px solid #dc2626;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #dc2626;
      padding: 15px 0;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #dc2626;
    }
    
    .address-section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .address-section h3 {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .address-section p {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 50px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 11px;
    }
    
    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }
    
    .status-completed {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: #16a34a;
    }
    
    .status-pending {
      background: #fef3c7;
      color: #b45309;
    }
    
    .status-cancelled {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: #dc2626;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="company-info">
        <h1>TechStore</h1>
        <p>Sản Phẩm Điện Tử & Công Nghệ</p>
        <p>Email: support@techstore.com</p>
      </div>
      <div class="invoice-title">
        <h2>HÓA ĐƠN</h2>
        <p>Đơn Hàng #<%= order.id %></p>
        <span class="status-badge status-<%= order.status %>"><%= order.status %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Meta Information -->
    <div class="invoice-meta">
      <div class="meta-section">
        <h3>Ngày Hóa Đơn</h3>
        <p><%= new Date(order.created_at).toLocaleDateString('vi-VN') %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-section">
        <h3>Mã Đơn Hàng</h3>
        <p>#<%= order.id %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Shipping Address -->
    <div class="address-section">
      <h3>Địa Chỉ Giao Hàng</h3>
      <p><%= order.shipping_address %></p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Items Table -->
    <div class="items-section">
      <h3>Các Mặt Hàng Đã Đặt</h3>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Tên Sản Phẩm</th>
            <th class="text-right">SKU</th>
            <th class="text-right">Số Lượng</th>
            <th class="text-right">Giá Đơn Vị</th>
            <th class="text-right">Tổng Tiền</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% if (items && items.length > 0) { %>
            <% items.forEach(item => { %>
              <tr>
                <td><%= item.name %></td>
                <td class="text-right">#<%= item.product_id %></td>
                <td class="text-right"><%= item.quantity %></td>
                <td class="text-right"><%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'VND' }).format(item.price / item.quantity) %></td>
                <td class="text-right"><%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'VND' }).format(item.price) %></td>
              </tr>
            <% }) %>
          <% } %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Summary -->
    <div class="summary-section">
      <div class="summary">
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span>Tổng Phụ:</span>
          <span><%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'VND' }).format(order.total_price / 1.1) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span>Thuế (10%):</span>
          <span><%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'VND' }).format(order.total_price / 1.1 * 0.1) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span>Vận Chuyển:</span>
          <span>Miễn Phí</span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row total">
          <span>Tổng Cộng:</span>
          <span><%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'VND' }).format(order.total_price) %></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Cảm ơn bạn đã mua hàng! Nếu có bất kỳ câu hỏi nào, vui lòng liên hệ với đội hỗ trợ của chúng tôi.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Được tạo lập vào <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('vi-VN') %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>